OL,3,CCumbria electricity network to double
OL,4,Cin capacity over next ten years
OL,6,FCumbria's electricity network capacity
OL,7,Fis set to double with half a billion
OL,8,Fpounds of investment.
OL,10,FSP Electricity North West has begun a
OL,11,Ften year programme of works to upgrade
OL,12,Fthe network known as the Cumbria Ring,
OL,13,Fwhich circles the county.
OL,15,FIn total, more than 150km of overhead
OL,16,Fline will be replaced, with the aim of
OL,17,Fenabling more renewable energy
OL,18,Fgeneration within Cumbria and allowing
OL,19,Ffor increased uptake of technologies
OL,20,Flike electric vehicles and heat pumps.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
