PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776445554
OL,3,CCumbria electricity network to double
OL,4,Cin capacity over next ten years
OL,6,FThe energy provider is already
OL,7,Funderway with phase 1 of the project,
OL,8,Fspending #56 million to replace the
OL,9,Flines and 152 pylons between Roosecote
OL,10,Fand Sellafield. This is expected to be
OL,11,Fcompleted by the end of this year.
OL,13,FVincent Cranny, SP Electricity North
OL,14,FWest's head of capital delivery, said:
OL,15,F"In what is a significant engineering
OL,16,Fproject involving hundreds of people,
OL,17,Four investment will strengthen the
OL,18,Fbackbone of the county's power network
OL,19,Fas the demand for electricity
OL,20,Fincreases.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776445554
OL,3,CCumbria electricity network to double
OL,4,Cin capacity over next ten years
OL,6,F"Once the whole of the Cumbria Ring is
OL,7,Fupgraded, capacity in the local
OL,8,Fnetwork will almost double enabling a
OL,9,Fclean affordable energy future. Homes
OL,10,Fand businesses will be able to adopt
OL,11,Flow carbon technologies at scale while
OL,12,Fallowing for future economic
OL,13,Fdevelopment for the region too."
OL,15,FThe pylons being replaced are each
OL,16,Fover 50 metres tall and weigh more
OL,17,Fthan 20 tonnes. While most can be
OL,18,Freplaced using cranes, the more remote
OL,19,Ftowers will need to be airlifted out
OL,20,Fby helicopter.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
