PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1776445554
OL,3,CCumbria electricity network to double
OL,4,Cin capacity over next ten years
OL,6,FJohn Barradell OBE, interim chief
OL,7,Fexecutive of the Cumbria Combined
OL,8,FAuthority, said: "This investment is
OL,9,Freally good news for Cumbria.
OL,10,FUpgrading our local power network at
OL,11,Fthis scale means our communities and
OL,12,Fbusinesses will have the energy
OL,13,Fcapacity they need for the future.
OL,15,F"This investment will help Cumbria
OL,16,Fgrow in a cleaner, greener way and
OL,17,Fmake sure we're ready for the shift to
OL,18,Flowcarbon technologies. It's a big
OL,19,Fstep forward for Cumbria's longterm
OL,20,Fprosperity and resilience."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
